extensionDescription.message: LinkedIn Container aislla l'actividá de LinkedIn pa evitar que te rastrexe fuera del so sitiu pente cookies de terceros.
extensionDescription.description: Description of the extension. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

in-fbc-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

in-fbc-p1.message: Agora LinkedIn pue rastrexate nesti sitiu. Pa quitalu de LinkedIn Container, esbilla «Sitios permitíos» en LinkedIn Container y quítalu de la llista.

on-facebook-p1.message: Esti iconu apaez na barra de direiciones de Firefox cuando visites sitios que pertenezan a LinkedIn o qu'amestares a LinkedIn Container.
on-facebook-p1.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

on-facebook-p2.message: Estos sitios precisen acceder a la to indentidá de LinkedIn (o saber quién yes) pa funcionar. Eso tamién significa que LinkedIn pue rastrexar tolo que faes nellos.
on-facebook-p2.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop up when the user is on LinkedIn.

notOnLinkedInHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

notOnLinkedInText.message: Esti sitiu ta fuera de LinkedIn Container. Esto dificulta a LinkedIn el rastrexate pente la rede.
notOnLinkedInText.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

onUnknownSiteHeader.message: Esti sitiu nun ta en LinkedIn Container.
onUnknownSiteHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on an "unknown" website - e.g., about:newtab. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

facebookContainer.description: This is the name of the extension, and appears at the top of all onboarding panels. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container".

onboarding1-p1.message: LinkedIn pue rastrexar el to restolar acullá de LinkedIn.com. Por exemplu, los botones Préstame o Compartir puen siguite hasta onde teas, tamién nos sitios nos que nun los usares.
onboarding1-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding1-p2.message: LinkedIn Container crea una llende ente los sitios de LinkedIn y el restu de la web pa que LinkedIn nun lo tenga fácil nel momentu de rastrexate en llinia.

onboarding2-p1.message: Esti iconu apaez na barra de direiciones de Firefox cuando visites sitios, como LinkedIn.com, que tean na llende de LinkedIn Container.
onboarding2-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the second onboarding panel.

onboarding2-p2.message: Estos sitios precisen acceder a la to indentidá de LinkedIn (o saber quién yes) pa funcionar. Eso tamién significa que LinkedIn pue rastrexar tolo que faes nellos.
onboarding2-p2.description: This is the second paragraph of the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding4-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-p1.message: Magar que nun teas en LinkedIn, LinkedIn pue rastrexate en llinia. Los botones que te dexen espublizar coses en LinkedIn o aniciar sesión nos sitios web col usu d'una cuenta de LinkedIn contienen rastrexadores. LinkedIn Container va boquiar esos rastrexadores y amosar l'iconu de valla pa enseñate onde se quitaron rastrexadores.
onboarding4-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-img.message: Esta imaxe demuestra cómo va apaecer l'iconu de valla de LinkedIn Container al llau d'un botón Préstame de LinkedIn.
onboarding4-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the fourth onboarding panel.

btn-cancel.description: This is a button to cancel out of the onboarding panel.

no-trackers-p1.message: LinkedIn Container nun deteutó nengún rastrexador de LinkedIn nesta páxina. Por embargu, la páxina pue contener otres tribes de rastrexadores.

how-fbc-works.description: This is a button that opens the LinkedIn Container onboarding flow.

trackers-detected-subhead.description: This is a subhead, and it means that the add on has protected the user by blocking LinkedIn trackers.

trackers-detected-p1.message: Los botones de LinkedIn qu'apaecen nes tiendes, noticies y otros sitios contienen rastrexadores que-y dicen a LinkedIn en que parte de la web tuviesti. Magar qu'enxamás usares esos botones pa prestar o compartir, los rastrexadores entá puen recoyer datos tocante al to restolar. LinkedIn Container blóquialos.

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-p2.message: Si quies usar l'aniciu de sesión con LinkedIn, LinkedIn va ser a rastrexar la to actividá nesti sitiu. Esto pue ayudalos a crear un perfil completu de la to vida dixital.
